data.description: BLACK FRIDAY SALE ***ONLY THIS Friday/Saturday ***Seller's Offering EXTRA $10K OFF of Sales Price!*** (MUST be under contract by midnight on Saturday!)  ***SELLERS OFFERING $10K TOWARD INCENTIVE OF BUYER'S CHOICE!***  With the holidays right around the corner, this turn-key house is ready for you to call home!  Enjoy the convenience of being located in the desirable gated community of the Shavano Bend Subdivision: walking distance to Clark High School; 5 minutes to HEB, restaurants and shopping; 10 minutes to Six Flags, LaCantera and Medical Center!  Meticulous up-grades: custom shelving and window coverings, crown molding and fresh paint throughout; granite countertops with matching dining and living room tables; walk-in pantry/laundry room with sliding barn door; ALL appliances convey (fridge x2, stove/oven, dishwasher, microwave, trash compactor, washer and dryer) and furniture is negotiable.  Master Bedroom and Home Office/Bonus Room with Murphy Doors downstairs, with loft and all secondary bedrooms upstairs, to include a newly installed en-suite!  Functional garage:  includes shelving, water softener (owned) and insulated garage door.  With BOTH HVAC's replaced in 2019, newer roof and minor foundation adjustment in 2009 (prior to current owners and NO further issues since "initial/ONLY" repair) and  Lifetime Transferrable Warranty in place (for foundation only), offers peace of mind.  Capture new memories on the largest lot in the neighborhood:  includes aesthetic Cabana, over-sized Chicken Coup/Run (fenced), with RV gate, STILL allowing plenty room for a pool and additional dwelling (see Survey attached); additional parking (only temporary; not conveyed with the home) located right beside the backyard fence and a door on the gate for alternate access!  Life is short:  laugh and ugly-cry over the reminiscence of the past and yearly generational traditions, while reviving them and making new memories with family and friends for years to come!
